reviews.text:
First off i am honored you would take inspiration from a recipe of mine! By now we both understand eachothers love for the flv tropicals.&#xD;
Very well balanced recipe, if you asked me to pick out what was in it just by taste i would not be able to. I know these flavors well but here they just mend so good together. I do understand what these flavors are doing to eachother even though nothing pops out too much in my face. &#xD;
Flv greek yogurt can get weird and too tangy for me sometimes, here it adds just the right amount of tang or "twang". &#xD;
Def a great mix, as per your recommendation i added a touch of fa polar blast just so the yogurt wouldnt get too weird for me.&#xD;
Great job jbird!
